                    <div class="container-4">
                        <div class="content-4" data-aos="zoom-in-right">
                            <div class="header-4">
                                <h2>Why Students Love Our Platform</h2>
                            </div>
                            <div class="red-line"></div>
                            <div class="text-4">
                                <p>We make it easy for students to discover real job opportunities from local employers,
                                    all
